-- Allen Stanford pleads not guilty to fraud charges
-- 
-- Thu Jun 25, 2009 12:28pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/06/25/us-stanford-court-idUSTRE55O2ZD20090625

 

 HOUSTON  (Reuters) - Texas financier Allen Stanford pleaded not guilty on Thursday to federal criminal charges that he masterminded a $7 billion fraud. 

 "Not guilty, Your Honor," Stanford told U.S. Magistrate Judge Frances Stacy. (Reporting by  Anna Driver  and  Eileen O'Grady  in Houston; Editing by Lisa Von Ahn)